                Hello There!
                 This is...
                PROJECT LAIRE
-----------------------------------------------

It is something like a platform for experimental
CLI apps. You can use the built-in apps for fun
and experimenting.

I really enjoy building these apps, and I think
you will too...

-----------------------------------------------

                Installation

Put the tar.gz package into a folder. Extract
the tar.gz file as folder. Open the folder and
execute the compile.sh script, and enjoy your
new Laire session!

----------------------------------------------

             Supporting the Project

I'm not taking any money. If you want to support
the project, you can request ideas and request
contributions.

----------------------------------------------

Sincerely,
Mertbikoss.
